    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Chinese porcelain in a famille rose style, painted with ruby ​​red enamel on the underside. It was first manufactured during the reign of Emperor Yongzheng (1723-1735).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
